title: Hearts of Iron 1 Soundtrack [192 kb/s]
description:
Couldn't find this on TPB yet, so decided to upload it.  Great music from a great game.  Music pulled straight from game files, mp3 at 192 kb/s @ 44000 hz.  I fixed the metadata ID3 tags so they are consistent (before they had these strange numbers that didn't identify the song or its composer).
